      </tr>
      <tr class="nhsuk-table__row">
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell ">NHS service standard</td>
        <td class="nhsuk-table__cell">Updated the <a href="/service-standard">NHS service standard</a> to make it clearer how it supports the GOV.UK service standard</td>
